Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA为何会如此美好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家为何会如此美好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为 大家都在心中收藏着美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 我还想继续与更多的人邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 昨天的一场雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让今天的威尼斯披上了雪白的外衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像为迎接即将到来的新年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给城市换上的新装一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里姐姐 AQUA很远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想更深地去体会那里夏日的炎热和冬天的寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但AQUA实在太远 我一个人无法前往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪白的新威尼斯 一定很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 我过去也有过跟小爱一样的想法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我 是那时的我想要成为的我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.30,0:01:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 差不多到时间去参加共同练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门了 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:38.23,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(320,280)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 雪白的温馨城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 蓝华 香草茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:03:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直温暖到心里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这雪下得还真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个晚上就积了这么厚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像新威尼斯城重生了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听到「啊～」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 灯里小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 蓝华 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们小时候想要变成什么样的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 突然问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是突然想到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能没太想过这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小后辈还是小孩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已经不是爱哭鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也已经不是爱哭鬼了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目标 果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像艾莉西亚前辈一样的优雅女性啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又会被晃前辈骂的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为领航员的话 我还是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但艾莉西亚前辈还是我憧憬的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也要变成艾莉西亚前辈那样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学别人 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你可别小看了艾莉西亚前辈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要变成那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要相当的努力和毅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白吗 毅力哦 毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里你没有的吧 毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在想别的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈以前想变成什么样的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是个优雅的大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如我们去散步吧 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,积了这么厚的雪 大概不会有客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就打烊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么出发啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又开始有点冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…好暖和…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:06:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暖包包 送给灯里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 灯里你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 这条路还没有人走过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是第一名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈小时候想成为什么样的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得很大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 叔叔也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚到这么大应该够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不谢不谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…那艾莉西亚前辈想变成什么样的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 不好意思 那个雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以加入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次滚这么大的雪球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了 我玩得非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上坡路很难滚呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 要用力推哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆到哪都不会丢人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢二位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有路了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:13:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我们马上把它移走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 不用不用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就放在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次见到这么大的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你们俩做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多人都帮过忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那也让我们来帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要玩～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领航员小姐们 累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:13:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝点暖和的饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真的 好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用 很暖和的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 纯白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是白可可哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用白巧克力做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手一定很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在做三明治哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃点小蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也去帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要玩得太疯喊腰痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说啥 这个不疯怎么行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要把它弄得更大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我们再多做一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 三弹吗 不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 刚才的领航员小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经滚得这么大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也在帮忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那爸爸也再来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么帮忙啊 这本来就是领航员小姐的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好像是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领航员小姐真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了就用这个来装饰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装饰装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊对了 我还有些好看的布头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是滚雪球 却能邂逅很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得自己被大家所温暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越来越喜欢这个城市了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雪的时候 我总是会去滚雪球玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始滚雪球啊 总是会有人跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起帮我把雪球越滚越大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到最后 大家都会很满足地回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时侯啊 我突然想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想变成那样的大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个微笑 就如水之精灵一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有这么一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记了时间的流逝 看得入了迷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈果然是个美好的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然说这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你与我相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给了我这么难能可贵的邂逅的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔地守护着我的这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里姐姐 我长大以后一定要去新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候灯里姐姐一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪白的城市非常美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像艾莉西亚小姐一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 AQUA今天也很和平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有在感谢本大爷吗 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿帕爷爷 有人送了好吃的年糕给我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我也继续在空中遨游
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要世界上还存在包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 蓝华 我们去吃披萨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 晃前辈请客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可以考虑请你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 太好了 我去我去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 总有一天我会要你加倍奉还
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你成为正式领航员之后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 天气暖和起来后 我们去野餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.17,0:22:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.61,0:22:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密 不过是个很好的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.11,0:22:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:22:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那灯里想变成什么样的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候想要成为精灵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.26,0:23:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 自由地在世界上飞舞 让大家都得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.47,0:23:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里马上也能成为精灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:45.24,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1400,0)\blur9\be1\fsp2\an2}希望 这座城市的温馨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.24,0:23:47.87,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1400,0)\blur9\be1\fsp2\an2}能够传达到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.87,0:23:54.45,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1400,2400)\blur9\be1\fsp2\an2}许多人的心中…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:02:03.47,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:17.62,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:33.33,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:46.78,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:55.95,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:04.26,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:12.60,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:16.21,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:24.25,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:02:03.47,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:17.62,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}洒落在 舒睡的睫毛间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:33.33,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}让轻拂的风吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:46.78,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}枝叶间滑落的阳光 映衬你的睡颜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:55.95,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}虽是个平凡无奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:04.26,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艳丽的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:12.60,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是与你邂逅的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:16.21,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我并非孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:24.25,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}因为 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:00.84,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}手のひらの上に そっとのせた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:08.35,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}やさしさを あたためて そっと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:12.19,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}口ずさんだ 秘密のメロヂィー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:20.23,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}歌ってよ 行くあてもないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:24.30,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}でも 降り出した雨も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:30.84,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}気にしない ずっとそばにいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:39.55,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いくつもの虹 越えて行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:42.99,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ふたりで オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:50.66,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}小さな光 星に願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:56.07,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}叶えてよ きっと 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:24.03,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いくつもの虹 越えて行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:27.70,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ふたりで オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:35.37,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}小さな光 星に願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:38.78,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}叶えてよ きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:46.55,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}描いてた夢 叶えられるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:49.85,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつかは オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:57.66,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雨上がりの虹 見上げた空に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:03.60,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}はばたいて いつか 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:11.94,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}胸いっぱいの愛を 集めてよ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:18.72,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}心にはいつも愛を 越えてくわ きっとレインボー
