Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:00.84,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}把悄然落在手心的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:08.35,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}细细地 温暖在怀中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:12.19,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}口中吟唱着神秘的曲调
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:20.23,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}吟唱着 失去了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:24.30,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}可是 那飘落的雨滴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:30.84,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}却不能影响我 因为有你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:39.55,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}穿过了 无数的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:42.99,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我们 一起越过彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:50.66,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}一点微光 向星星许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:56.07,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}相信那青鸟 定会为我实现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:24.03,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}穿过了 无数的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:27.70,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我们 一起越过彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:35.37,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}一点微光 向星星许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:38.78,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}梦想 定会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:46.55,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}所有的梦想 都将实现
